{"tid":1051242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實麥記依家係未轉型左做庇護工場","createTime":"2019-03-07T12:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T13:53:13.000Z","uid":12211,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a33577857a24ea4e5af843bb0413a6b281050bb9","tid":1051242,"uid":12211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩落樓買個麥樂雞餐食<br />\n<br />\n眼見成間麥記五六個員工，得收銀嗰個係正常。<br />\n<br />\n執餐嗰幾個係咁倒瀉野，基本上佢比客人嘅所有食物都會整冧，搞到個counter 同埋地下全部都係薯條同汽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清潔嗰個就慢到蝸牛咁，我見佢成五分鐘都未執好一個盤。基本上依家成間麥記，差唔多冇一個位係乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n真係好佩服正常果個員工，日日返工對住佢哋幾個都真係唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbec4bee8d1ea39ae9cd10e4ac101b4634757a2","tid":1051242,"uid":233267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"M記呢排都見唔到有比較年輕嘅妹妹做 全部都係講東話都講唔正嘅呀姐"},{"pid":"f6629cecd9c00ecdc8b4e5ab1bb5f2a48a62027b","tid":1051242,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正仆街，人地已經好慘，俾條生路佢地行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10094a6c8dfa4eb95812000a33c94f74274d8e17","tid":1051242,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"向美國，墨西哥人多"},{"pid":"319c27d46d9b6f6ec5fe55cabda6aeac9e6dcce8","tid":1051242,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"KFC咪仲衰"},{"pid":"9daf1c94cc4b8dbcf4e49fa4e7c6b160893ba2bc","tid":1051242,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"